<DocsLayout 
  title="Get Started" 
  description="Learn the basics and start building with AgentOps"
  section="Get Started"
>
  <DocsSidebar slot="sidebar" />
  
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        AgentOps is built on OpenTelemetry, the industry standard for observability.
        This means you get powerful tracing, monitoring, and evaluation capabilities
        without vendor lock-in.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>What You'll Learn</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>How to instrument your AI applications with OpenTelemetry</li>
        <li>Core concepts like traces, spans, and observations</li>
        <li>How to run evaluations and experiments</li>
        <li>Managing prompts and deployments</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Next Steps</h2>
      <div class="not-prose space-y-3">
        <a href="/docs/get-started/quickstart" class="block p-4 bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 hover:border-primary-500 transition-colors">
