          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Get up and running in 5 minutes</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/docs/get-started/core-concepts" class="block p-4 bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 hover:border-primary-500 transition-colors">
